{
  "title": "Buttery Irish Beetroot Bowl",
  "description": "A tender, buttery beetroot bowl featuring slow-cooked beets with a creamy dairy-free topping, perfect for meal prep. This egg-free dish is rich with natural sweetness and fiber.",
  "cuisine": "irish",
  "diet": [
    "egg-free",
